content: I want to dedicate 5 days a week to exercise. My available time slots are mornings and evenings, except for Tuesdays and Thursdays when I have Pilates classes. I've been enjoying my dance classes on weekends, so I'd like to keep those. I've also been taking short walks during my lunch break and trying to get back into cycling on Sundays. My fitness goals are to improve flexibility, endurance, and overall well-being.
